1776818001590917	kb-dev	itc:v3:AWLJ58k-Zk8zEAAAAAAAQde-r7a9sAAAAAEt3QY		item.create	bn-2wyt	{"description":"kb init creates 11 subdirs that no compile/ingest/ask path ever writes to. Repro: kb init, kb ingest notes/, kb compile — wiki/people, wiki/projects, wiki/timelines, outputs/reports, outputs/slides, outputs/figures, raw/papers, raw/datasets, raw/images, reviews/aliases, reviews/canonicalization are all still empty.\n\nRemove them from the init scaffold. Keep what's actually used: raw/{inbox,web}, wiki/{concepts,sources}, outputs/questions, reviews/{promotions,merges}. On-demand review kinds (contradictions, concept_candidates, imputed_fixes) are created by their writers via create_dir_all when the first item lands.","kind":"task","title":"chore(init): stop scaffolding dead empty directories in kb init"}	blake3:ehirSgjaaeGVAIWhhVT9_Rn6LlRK04jdlGKcDyaSt68
