1776879876556590	kb-dev	itc:v3:AWLJ58k-Zk8zEAAAAAAAQde-r7a9sAAAAAEt6AY		item.comment	bn-nlw9	{"body":"Phases 1-7 done. 5 commits on bn-nlw9 workspace. Adds slug_for_filename helper to kb-core, source_page_path_for/clean_stale_source_pages/resolve_source_page_path to kb-compile::source_page, resolve_question_dir to kb-query::paths and kb-cli::id_resolve. Compile now writes wiki/sources/<src-id>-<title-slug>.md and cleans stale variants; kb ask writes outputs/questions/q-<id>-<slug>/. kb migrate Phase B renames legacy id-only files/dirs and refreshes backlinks. All 845 tests + clippy pass. Ready for review/merge."}	blake3:a632bb56EHpz2tDeE3Fe8ZlEyx80rV8RKwW1b5-BdmE
